The paper discusses the decoding algorithm for polar codes, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the implementation complexity and energy consumption, which are topics related to systems and control (cs.SY) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper proposes a new decoding algorithm, which involves partitioning, a technique that is related to data structures (cs.DS) and computational complexity (cs.CC).
